Name: x_f_release
Description: 1 if feature is selected into the next release

Name: x_us_sprint
Description: 1 if user story u is assigned to sprint s (indexed by u,s)

Name: x_task_team
Description: 1 if task k is assigned to team t (indexed by k,t)

Name: x_worker_team
Description: 1 if worker w belongs to team t (indexed by w,t)

Name: x_worker_role
Description: 1 if worker w takes role r (indexed by w,r)

Name: x_blocker_resolve
Description: 1 if blocker bl is resolved for task k (indexed by k,bl)

Name: x_budget_project
Description: Allocated budget for project p (indexed by p)

Name: x_sprint_goal_achieve
Description: 1 if sprint s is planned to achieve its goal

Name: x_team_project
Description: 1 if team t is assigned to project p (indexed by t,p)

Name: x_doc_use
Description: 1 if feature documentation fed is linked/used (indexed by fed)

Name: x_sm_support
Description: 1 if Scrum Master sm supports team t (indexed by sm,t)

Name: x_po_pb
Description: 1 if Product Owner po manages Product Backlog pb (indexed by po,pb)

Name: x_team_sprint
Description: 1 if team t works on sprint s (indexed by t,s)

Name: x_review_active
Description: 1 if sprint review sr is scheduled
